Jacques Sablon https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacques_Sablon 0 Jacques Sablon (March 1906, Nogent-sur-Marne – 24 February 1994, Cannes) was a 20th-century French film actor. He was the grandson of actor Gustave Hamilton, the nephew of singers Jean Sablon and Germaine Sablon and the cousin of actress Berthe Jalabert.
